# Quartz Repository Rules

## Branch Rules
- Main branch: `v4`
- Protected branch: requires PR, no direct pushes
- Always create feature branches: `feat/*`, `fix/*`, etc.

## Workflow
- Pull before work: repo changes frequently
- Create PR -> merge to v4
- GitHub Actions deploys to gh-pages on v4 branch pushes
- Submodules need recursive update after pull

## Project
- Static site generator for digital garden/notes
- Base URL: articles.kirill-markin.com
- Uses submodules (_obsidian) 